                <p>Frame sustainability as a strategic business advantage with concrete benefits:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Risk reduction and operational resilience:</strong> Help businesses prepare for resource constraints and market changes</li>
                    <li><strong>Cost efficiency and resource optimization:</strong> Identify opportunities to reduce expenses through smarter resource use</li>
