            <div class="implementation-notes">
                <h3>Implementation Approach</h3>
                <p>When implementing these changes, consider the following guidance:</p>

                <h4>1. Phased Implementation</h4>
                <p>Introduce green elements gradually over several cohorts:</p>
                <div class="timeline">
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h3>Phase 1: Quick Wins</h3>
                            <p>Implement the simplest changes that require minimal adaptation:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Updated pitch examples</li>
                                <li>Enhanced user persona template</li>
                                <li>New judging criteria</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-content">
